        </div>
        <div class="grid-img">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1567966456076-905a50a06d8c?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8NXx8ZHJlc3Nlc3xlbnwwfHwwfHw%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=60"
            alt=""
          />
          <div class="img-info">
            <a href="/products/category/dresses"
              ><p>Check out more dresses</p></a
